{"type":"click","text":"A\n    \n      Extend the PHP backend (Recommended)\n      Add OAuth2 (Discord + Google), sessions, and write endpoints directly to the existing PHP backend. New admin UI pages added to the Vite app at /admin.\n      \n        Pros\n          Single backend to deploy and maintain\n          Consistent with existing shared-host deployment\n          No new runtime dependencies\n        \n        Cons\n          PHP OAuth libraries are more verbose than JS equivalents\n          api.php grows larger (mitigated by splitting into files)","choice":"a","id":null,"timestamp":1773771481089}
